<% content_for :title, "About Us - Spotlight OS" %>
<% content_for :description, "Learn about Spotlight OS, our mission to transform sales with AI-powered voice technology, and the team behind the platform." %>

<!-- About Hero Section -->
<section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        About 
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Spotlight OS
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We're revolutionizing how businesses connect with customers through AI-powered voice technology 
        that transforms every conversation into an opportunity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          At Spotlight OS, we believe that every customer interaction should be meaningful, timely, and effective. 
          Traditional sales processes often miss opportunities due to limited availability, inconsistent messaging, 
          or human error.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our AI-powered voice platform ensures that no lead goes unqualified, no appointment goes unbooked, 
          and no customer goes unheard. We're not replacing human connection – we're amplifying it.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Innovation First</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Cutting-edge AI technology that adapts to your business needs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 p-8 rounded-2xl text-white">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Impact</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Businesses Served</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">2,500+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Conversations Handled</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">1M+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Average ROI Increase</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">340%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <span>Customer Satisfaction</span>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold">98%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Story Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Our Story</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
      <p class="mb-6">
        Spotlight OS was born from a simple observation: businesses were losing countless opportunities 
        because they couldn't respond to prospects quickly enough, consistently enough, or at scale.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Our founders, experienced in both sales and AI technology, witnessed firsthand how manual processes 
        created bottlenecks that cost companies millions in lost revenue. They envisioned a world where 
        AI could handle the initial qualification and scheduling, freeing human sales professionals to focus 
        on what they do best – building relationships and closing deals.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-8">
        Today, Spotlight OS powers sales conversations for thousands of businesses worldwide, from startups 
        to Fortune 500 companies, helping them capture more leads, qualify prospects faster, and scale their 
        sales operations without scaling their headcount.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Values Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">The principles that guide everything we do</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Value 1 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Customer Success</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Your success is our success. We're committed to delivering measurable results that drive your business forward.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Value 2 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Innovation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We continuously push the boundaries of what's possible with AI technology to stay ahead of the curve.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Value 3 -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
